                        Personal Data of minors.
16.2 If you are a minor, you may not use Plerdy Tools.
16.3 Plerdy has the right to delete the Personal Data of a minor, without warning and any
                        consequences for the Platform, and to terminate the provision of such person to the Tools.
16.4 If you have information about the use of the Tools by a minor, please contact Platform
                        support by sending an email to:
hello@plerdy.com
.
